text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt15Intro {
	"I don't have a bone to pick with you.
	I'm just following orders!"
}

text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt15Defeat {
	"I may have lost, but…"
}

text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt15PostBattle {
	"We dug up something beyond belief!
	And, we got the BLUE ORB!

	All that's left is for our leader to…
	Fufufu… Fwahahaha!"
}

text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt6Intro {
	"I can't stand heat. Maybe I should've
	joined TEAM AQUA instead…"
}

text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt6Defeat {
	"Yeah, I really may not be right for
	TEAM MAGMA…"
}

text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt6PostBattle {
	"Don't you get lonely for the sea
	being in a place like this?"
}

text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt7Intro {
	"You can hear tremors here sometimes.

	Could it be the volcano rattling?
	Or is it GROU…

	Whoops!
	No, no, never mind!"
}

text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt7Defeat {
	"You're a fiery battler.
	Just like a volcano!"
}

text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt7PostBattle {
	"You just happened to win this time,
	but that doesn't matter.

	TEAM MAGMA's goal is about to be
	reached!"
}

text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt8Intro {
	"One of our guys was freaking out that
	he lost his MAGMA EMBLEM…

	Wait a minute!
	Was it you who found it?"
}

text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt8Defeat {
	"I'm having trouble believing this…"
}

text MagmaHideout_2F_2R_Text_Grunt8PostBattle {
	"I'm getting this feeling that our plan
	is going to end in failure…"
}
